rows.label: qst701008_msg0001
rows.name:
Hey everyone! Kaede-chan and I managed
to collect this. I hope it helps.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0002
rows.name:
I'm sure there's still a lot left to do...
We want to help out in any way we can.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0003
rows.name: Let's get this shelter finished! Woo!

rows.label: qst701008_msg0101
rows.name:
I think I'll stay in the capital
for a bit and lend my dad a hand.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0102
rows.name:
Times are tough and I reckon folks
round here need all the help they
can get, right?

rows.label: qst701008_msg0103
rows.name:
I wouldn't have had the guts for this
before, but since my time in Gula
I feel like maybe I've grown a bit.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0104
rows.name:
Kaede-chan said that rather than worrying
about all the things you can't do, it's
better to focus on the things you can.
